__NUXT_JSONP__("/", (function(a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h,i,j,k,l,m,n,o,p,q,r){return {data:[{articles:[{slug:"First_blog",title:"Poukisa mwen kreye Blog sa?",date:k,description:"Mwen kreye blog sila nan lide pou mwen pataje youn nan pi gwo pasyon ke mwen genyen ki se kode, pwogramasyon... Mwen paka detèmine kilè egzakteman pasyon sa a te anparem, men sèl sa mwen konnen depi mwen tou piti mwen te toujou renmen bagay ki genyen rapò avek teknoloji...  ",toc:[],body:{type:l,children:[{type:b,tag:m,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:d},{type:b,tag:n,props:{className:[o]},children:[{type:a,value:"Poukisa mwen kreye Blòg sa? "}]},{type:a,value:d},{type:b,tag:e,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:"\nMwen kreye blog sila nan lide pou mwen pataje youn nan pi gwo pasyon ke mwen genyen ki se kode, pwogramasyon... Mwen paka detèmine kilè egzakteman pasyon sa a te anparem, men sèl sa mwen konnen depi mwen tou piti mwen te toujou renmen bagay ki genyen rapò avek teknoloji, mwen te toujou renmen kreye, inove, epi le mwen vin dekouvri pwogramasyon mwen te vin reyalize ke se yon bon mwayen pou mwen mete kreyativitem nan travay epi yon mwayen tou pou mwen travay lojik mwen.\n"},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:d},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:d}]},{type:b,tag:e,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:"Blog la pwal fokis esansyèlaman sou mond pwogramasyon an, mwen pwal bay opinyon pam sou kek bagay nan disiplin nan, pataje eksperyans mwen, bagay estipid ak bagay jenyal ke mwen ap fè avek teknoloji ke mwen ap itilize yo.\n"},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:d},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]}]},{type:a,value:d},{type:b,tag:e,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:"Mwen pwal pataje tou sa yo rele an anglè a \"TIPS & TRICKS\" sou teknoloji ke mwen itilize deja yo ki se HTML, CSS , JAVASCRIPT, VUE.JS e nan yon fiti ki pwoch mwen pwal pataje kek bagay sou REACT.JS tou. Se yon fason pou mwen di nap okouran de o mwen on ti pati de jan map pwogrese nan mond tèk la.\n"},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:"\nMwen vrèman espere ke nou pwal li e pwofite de blog la. Pa ezite ban mwen kritik sou kontni ke mwen gen pou poste yo epitou di mwen ki fonksyonalite nou ta renmen we blog la genyen pou ou ka gen yon eksperyans ki pi konfotab avek li.\n"},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:d},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]}]},{type:a,value:d},{type:b,tag:e,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:"Mèsi anpil.\n"},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:"\nMwen espere ou apresye."}]},{type:a,value:d},{type:b,tag:e,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:d}]},{type:a,value:d},{type:b,tag:p,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:"\n.note{\n  color :red;\n  font-weight : bold;\n}\n\n\n.premye{\n  color:#63B3ED;\n  font-weight : bold;\n  font-size: 28px;\n  text-align : center;\n  padding-bottom : 20px;\n}\n\n  "}]}]},dir:q,path:"\u002Fblog\u002FFirst_blog",extension:r,createdAt:"2020-10-29T22:41:07.023Z",updatedAt:"2020-10-29T21:23:04.484Z"},{slug:"Second_blog",title:"Kijan mwen kreye blog sila?",date:k,description:f,toc:[],body:{type:l,children:[{type:b,tag:m,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:g},{type:b,tag:n,props:{className:[o]},children:[{type:a,value:"Kijan mwen kreye blòg sila?"}]},{type:a,value:g},{type:b,tag:e,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:" Blog sa a se yon pwojè ke mwen travay sou li ki fèm dekouvri potansyalite VUE.JS anpil. Framework sa jis ekselan."},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:g},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:" Ann swiv avèm. "},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:" Mwen sot di ke "},{type:b,tag:i,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:" VUE.JS "}]},{type:a,value:" ekselan men mwen poko pale de "},{type:b,tag:i,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:"Nuxt.js"}]},{type:a,value:", mwen kreye blog sa avek Nuxt ki se yon teknoloji ki baze sou  Vue.js."},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:f},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:" Poukisa mwen te chwazi Nuxt?"},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:" Etan done ke mwen kreye blog sa pou mwen pataje yon bon kantite atik sou li mwen te bezwen yon sòt de fonksyonalite ki rele "},{type:b,tag:j,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:"'Routing'"}]},{type:a,value:" pou mwen te ka pèmèt ou menm kom itilizatè pou te ka navige nan plizye paj ki nan blog la alèz. Pa egzanp pou li tèks sa a ou sot klike sou "},{type:b,tag:j,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:"\u002FLi plis "}]},{type:a,value:" li voye ou dirèkteman la a, e pou ou ale nan paj akèy la ou pwal klike sou blog pou ou ka wè tout atik yo. Nuxt te pèmèt  mwen jere sa ak yon fasilite enkwayab. Mwen pa di Vue pa jere sa, men Nuxt rann lavi devlope Vue yo pi fasil paske si ou tap fèl avèk vue ou ta pwal genyen bon 2, 3 kod pouw ekri. Men Nuxt li di pa okipew devlopè map jere sa pou ou otomatikaman."},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:f},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:" \n    "},{type:b,tag:"strong",props:{},children:[{type:a,value:" \n    Nuxt\u002FTailwindCSS "}]},{type:a,value:f},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:" Tout moun ki abitye pale avem de tèk konnen ke "},{type:b,tag:i,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:"TailwindCSS"}]},{type:a,value:" se yon frameworK CSS ke mwen pa negosye(Aba Bootstrap).  Mwen kreye blog la avèk Tailwind tou pou mwen te ka mete stil mwen vle e fè sit la byen parèt nan prèske tout aparèy avek fasilite (mobile & Deskto). "},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:" Poukisa Tailwind? "},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:" Repons kout : Jis paske li pi bon. "}]},{type:b,tag:"blockquote",props:{className:["twitter-tweet"]},children:[{type:b,tag:e,props:{lang:"en",dir:"ltr"},children:[{type:b,tag:h,props:{href:"https:\u002F\u002Ftwitter.com\u002Fadamwathan?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"},children:[{type:a,value:"@adamwathan"}]},{type:a,value:" Tailwind CSS is the best man, thank you and to anyone else who helped build this, such an epic tool. Ever since starting with Laravel, the community, support, knowledge, and tooling is just next level, so intuitive and user friendly. "},{type:b,tag:h,props:{href:"https:\u002F\u002Ftwitter.com\u002Fhashtag\u002Fconvert?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"},children:[{type:a,value:"#convert"}]}]},{type:a,value:"— Sam Webster (@Sam_Webster) "},{type:b,tag:h,props:{href:"https:\u002F\u002Ftwitter.com\u002FSam_Webster\u002Fstatus\u002F1243685813637902337?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"},children:[{type:a,value:"March 27, 2020"}]}]},{type:a,value:f},{type:b,tag:"script",props:{async:true,src:"https:\u002F\u002Fplatform.twitter.com\u002Fwidgets.js",charSet:"utf-8"},children:[]},{type:a,value:g},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:" Repons long : Mwen sonje yon lè mwen avèk frèm nan tap gade yon sit epi misye di: \"Hmm sit sa fèt avèk bootstrap kanmenm\". Se yon fason pou mwen diw majorite sit bootstrap yo sanble, paske li ofriw bagay ki deja dizay se modifye ou pwal modifye, se sa an gwo moun kap itilize Bootstrap yo fè (kopye\u002Fkole\u002Fmodifye). Men Tailwind li di non, fok devlopè yo gen lib chwa pou dizay sit yo jan yo vle, sa nap fè nou menm nap jis bay yo sa yo rele yon "},{type:b,tag:j,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:" \"low-level Utility Classes\""}]},{type:a,value:". 'Low-level utility classes' yo pa elwanyew de 'Plain CSS' si ou itilize Tailwind pou on bon tan lèw tounen nan PLAIN CSS wap we se tankou ou pat janm kitel. M pap pale plis poum pa fe yon liv sou Framework sa paske map ekri atik sa a mwen tou eksite, map envite ou vizite li =\u003E "},{type:b,tag:h,props:{href:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.tailwindcss.com\u002F",target:"_blank"},children:[{type:a,value:"TailwindCSS!"}]},{type:a,value:f},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:" Epi sam renmen an  pandan wap kode sit ou an avek HTML wap tou pase class tailwind ou yo, ou pa bezwen kreye yon fichye CSS."},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:" \n    An konklizyon se sou tèk sa yo (Nuxt & Tailwind) ke sit sa ap woule, e nan pwochen atik kap vini m pwal pale sou yo plis. "},{type:b,tag:c,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:"\n    Enjoy!! \n    "},{type:b,tag:e,props:{},children:[]},{type:a,value:d}]},{type:a,value:d},{type:b,tag:p,props:{},children:[{type:a,value:"\n\n.premye{\n  color:#63B3ED;\n  font-weight : bold;\n  font-size: 28px;\n  text-align : center;\n  padding-bottom : 20px;\n}\n\nem{\n    border-bottom : 1px dotted #63B3ED;\n}\n\ncode{\n    background-color : #63B3ED;\n    border-radius : 7px;\n    padding: 2px; \n}\n\na{\n     border-bottom : 1px solid #63B3ED;\n}\n\n\n"}]}]},dir:q,path:"\u002Fblog\u002FSecond_blog",extension:r,createdAt:"2020-10-29T22:41:07.029Z",updatedAt:"2020-10-29T21:23:18.747Z"}]}],fetch:[],mutations:void 0}}("text","element","br","\n","p"," ","\n    ","a","code","em","2020-09-21T11:51:59.091Z","root","div","h1","premye","style","\u002Fblog",".md")));